"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1930307-Olympics-2024-Olympic-village-Sam-Quek\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Olympics 2024athletes have been booted out of the Olympic village after their events in a bid to avoid the spread of Covid-19.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The policy change was introduced in Tokyo three years ago and has remained in place in Paris.\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 165, \"end\": 170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999725160507981, \"rank\": 2.7481527813517193e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.8109299580380265e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes from all across the world have been staying in the Olympic village, which is located five miles north of Paris and spans Saint-Ouen, Saint-Denis, and L'Ile-Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.8109299580380265e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is housing a total of 14,250 athletes during the Olympics and another 8,000 during the Paralympics.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And former Olympian Sam Quek, who won a gold medal as part of Great Britain's hockey team at Rio 2016, has offered an insight into life in the village.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999997530699453, \"rank\": 2.4693004986506095e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 527, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Quek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\"}, {\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7893247414532609, \"rank\": 0.2648725066792513, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So this is a bit of a breaking news situation,\\\" Quek toldCapital Breakfast.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Normally at the Olympics you stay at the village from the beginning to the end and everyone stays and then goes home.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But for some reason this year they have remained in place the same rules they had in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999725160507981, \"rank\": 2.7481527813517193e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because of Covid when they finished, they had to leave